{1: '1', 2: 'Bai Gui', 3: 'It seems like we failed to bring down Babylonia.', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Qu', 3: "That's fine. I've never wanted to end human suffering that way, anyway.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Qu', 3: 'When a plan fails, we just move on to the next one.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Qu', 3: "I have all the time in the world now that I'm behind the scenes.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bai Gui', 3: 'So are you still trying to think of a way to kill all humans in an instant without putting them through pain?', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Qu', 3: 'I would have said "yes" in the past without a moment\'s hesitation.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Qu', 3: "But after what happened this time, I can't be so sure anymore.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bai Gui', 3: 'Is it because of that team?', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Qu', 3: 'Yes. I thought they would choose to save more people and avenge those who died at the hand of their enemy.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Qu', 3: 'But they chose a totally different path and missed such a perfect opportunity.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Qu', 3: "They've paid such a heavy price for their choice and lived through such pain, but they still stay on the frontline of the war and never give in.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Qu', 3: 'They are so miserable and fragile, yet they still shine in all their beauty.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Qu', 3: "Old ideas probably aren't meant to work anymore.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Qu', 3: "It's probably time that we adjust Tabula Akasha accordingly.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Bai Gui', 3: "(Nods) I think you'll find your answer.", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Bai Gui', 3: 'No matter what happens, you will always have our support.', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Qu', 3: "Well... Let's put aside these issues with humans for now.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Qu', 3: 'Luna must be eliminated no matter how Tabula Akasha evolves.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Qu', 3: "Let's see through our deal first, little Murray from Babylonia.", 4: '1'}
